❄️👸🏼🌸

Once, upon a snowy mountain, lived a little girl named Snow White. 🏔️❄️👧🏼
She had skin as white as snow, lips as red as blood, and hair as black as night. 🧊👄🩸🌑
Her seven dwarfs lived in a cozy cottage nearby. 🏠🔨🌲
One day, the Evil Queen saw Snow White in the mirror. 🪞👑👀
"Who is the fairest of them all?" she asked. 🤔
The mirror replied, "You are, my queen." 🙋‍♀️✨
The Queen grew jealous and angry. 😡🔥
She disguised herself as an old woman and offered Snow White a poisoned apple. 🍎👵🏼🍂
Snow White took a bite, but the poison didn't work immediately. 🤤🍏❌
The Queen ran away, laughing maniacally. 😈🏃‍♀️🤪
Snow White fell into a deep sleep. 😴💤🌑
The dwarfs found her and placed her in a glass coffin. 🪟🪦🥀
Years passed, and the Queen grew old and gray. 👵🏼👴🏼🌫️
One day, a prince rode through the forest. 🐎👑🌲
He saw the sleeping Snow White and felt a strange pull. 🤩👀
He kissed her gently, and the poison vanished! 💋✨🚫
Snow White woke up, smiling brightly. 😊🌞👸🏼
The Queen was overjoyed to see her again. 😍👑🎉
And they lived happily ever after. 🏰💑🌈🎶 [end of text]


